    "Appropriations ($)",
    "Economic Diversification Strategic Plan",
    "HTDC",
    "STEM Education Outreach Program",
    "Small Business Innovation Research Matching Program"
  ],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Requires the Hawaii Technology Development Corporation to establish the Small Business Innovation Research Matching Program.  Requires the Hawaii Technology Development Corporation, in collaboration with the Department of Education, to establish a STEM education outreach program.  Requires and appropriates funds for the Hawaii Technology Development Corporation to develop an economic diversification strategic plan.  Appropriates funds for economic diversification and defense ecosystem development."
    }
  ],
